<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; -qt-user-state:0;"><span style=" font-family:'Lucida Console'; font-size:8pt;">  vec3 front = normalize(screenCenter - eye);</span></p>
